<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>classical on Hugo-HT</title><link>https://yangxingyue0623.github.io/categories/classical/</link><description>Recent content in classical on Hugo-HT</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Oct 1925 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yangxingyue0623.github.io/categories/classical/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>背影</title><link>https://yangxingyue0623.github.io/cn/1925/10/01/beiying/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Oct 1925 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yangxingyue0623.github.io/cn/1925/10/01/beiying/</guid><description>我父亲不相见已二年余了，我最不能忘记的是他的背影。那年冬天，祖母死了，父亲的差使也交卸了，正是祸不单行的日子，我从北京到徐州，打算跟着父亲奔丧回家。到徐州见着父亲，看见满院狼藉的东西，又想起祖母，不禁簌簌地流下眼泪。父亲说，“事已如此，不必难过，好在天无绝人之路！”</description></item></channel></rss>